LCF2XML
=======

LCF2XML is a small tool to convert RPG Maker 2000(3) data to XML and vice-versa.

LCF2XML is part of the EasyRPG Project. More information is available
at the project website:

  https://easy-rpg.org/


Documentation
-------------

Documentation is available at the documentation wiki:

  https://easy-rpg.org/wiki/


Requirements
------------

EasyRPG Readers library with XML enabled. https://github.com/EasyRPG/Readers
Expat for XML support.


Daily builds
------------

Up to date binaries for assorted platforms are available at:

  https://easy-rpg.org/jenkins/


Source code
-----------

LCF2XML development is hosted by GitHub.
Project files are available in Git repositories.

  https://github.com/EasyRPG/LCF2XML


Building
--------

* GNU C++ compiler method:

  Compile with:
  g++ src/main.cpp -I /ABSOLUTE/PATH/TO/Readers/build/include -L /ABSOLUTE/PATH/TO/Readers/build/lib -lreaders -lexpat -o LCF2XMLEXECUTABLENAME


* Visual Studio method:

  Read the lib/README file then open the solution file in builds/ folder.


